  "detailed_description": "Avoid is a fast-paced arcade game that will test your reflexes. Drive your vehicle through an obstacle-filled course and try to go as far as you can. Grab bonus items to help you survive... just a little bit more. Climb up the online leaderboard and show the world who's best! Are your fingers fast enough?<br />\n<br />\nFeatures:<br />\n<br />\n    Fast arcade game, easy to learn but difficult to master<br />\n    Challenging levels and a randomly generated endless mode<br />\n    Engaging visual effects and soundrack<br />\n    Online leaderboards<br />\n    Have we already mentioned that it's FAST?",
  "about_the_game": "Avoid is a fast-paced arcade game that will test your reflexes. Drive your vehicle through an obstacle-filled course and try to go as far as you can. Grab bonus items to help you survive... just a little bit more. Climb up the online leaderboard and show the world who's best! Are your fingers fast enough?<br />\n<br />\nFeatures:<br />\n<br />\n    Fast arcade game, easy to learn but difficult to master<br />\n    Challenging levels and a randomly generated endless mode<br />\n    Engaging visual effects and soundrack<br />\n    Online leaderboards<br />\n    Have we already mentioned that it's FAST?",
